{"tid":2343045,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中國區 Steam 平台即將啟用　內容審查遊玩時限樣樣齊","createTime":"2020-12-27T15:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T18:29:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5e277ee813a1f9a972da53253532a056037b865c","tid":2343045,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"Steam 全世界平台共通，不過因為中國政府的特殊監管需要，之前他們公佈與完美世界合作，建立中國特別版的「蒸汽平台」，最近終於公佈於明年 1 月 16 日開始測試。<br />\n<br />\n蒸汽平台將會為中國玩家特別提供本地服務和高速伺服器，並且配合政府的監管政策，防止沉迷遊玩，也會加入符合政府規定的內容管制，讓遊戲平台更加健康。平台上有大量網絡成癮警告和遊玩時間提醒標語，而且如果想要更改 ID 和頭像，都要經過審核。未成年玩家的遊戲時間也受到限制，直接在平台層面禁止時限外遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n由於 Steam 本來是少數未受嚴格管制的平台，今次官方中國版蒸汽平台推出後，相信中國玩家就無法連接原本的 Steam 平台。雖然中國媒體大力吹捧這個平台，但有中國網民表示擔心無法玩到想玩的遊戲，表示「我們就是一群打遊戲的，希望上層建築的人上人們放過我們」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/26/steam-china-2/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F26%2Fsteam-china-2%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd%2FolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=da37c4b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/26/steam-china-2/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"f38fb543d056ce6a83593e2906d23b67a9aabfc2","tid":2343045,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb7f407ec1495634ed0e5b0fe2f0aa900aa8082","tid":2343045,"uid":19454,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"相信中國玩家就無法連接原本的 Steam 平台<br />\n相信中國玩家就無法連接原本的 Steam 平台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass